data.description: Motivated Sellers!!!! Welcome to 105 Meadow Lake Drive! This inviting property boasts a spacious floorplan spanning just over 1900 sqft, providing ample room for your family to grow and make lasting memories. Upon entering, you are greeted by spacious living area. The well-lit living spaces offer a seamless flow, perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying quality time with loved ones. The master bath has granite countertops with double vanity, jet tub and shower. The three additional good-sized bedrooms share a bath. Don't forget about the BEAUTIFUL sunroom with water views to use as you see fit.  Step outside and enjoy your patio with PLENTY of space in your backyard. Less than 10 mins to I-85 for easy commuting. Whether you're relaxing on the front porch or exploring nearby, this is truly a place you'll be proud to call home. Don't miss the opportunity!
